      <b>Academy:</b> Includes anything related to
      <WikiLink page="Living Area#Canteen and Merchant">Merchant</WikiLink>,
      <WikiLink page="Living Area#Canteen and Merchant">Oil Canteen</WikiLink>,
      <WikiLink page="Living Area#Lecture Hall">Lecture Hall</WikiLink>,
      <WikiLink page="Commissions">Commissions</WikiLink>,
      <WikiLink page="Guild">Guilds</WikiLink>.
    </p>
  </li>
  <li>
    <p>
      <b>Missions:</b> Includes <WikiLink page="Missions#Login Rewards"
        >Login Rewards</WikiLink
      >,
      <WikiLink page="Missions#Daily Missions">Daily Missions</WikiLink>,
      <WikiLink page="Missions#Weekly Missions">Weekly Missions</WikiLink>,
      <WikiLink page="Beginner Rewards">Beginner Rewards</WikiLink>,
      <WikiLink page="Missions#One-Time Missions">One-Time Missions</WikiLink>
      (not including Secretary Quests).
    </p>
  </li>
  <li>
    <p>
      <b>Daily Raid:</b> Includes all stages listed
      <WikiLink page="Daily Raid">here</WikiLink>.
    </p>
  </li>
  <li>
    <p>
      <b>Cruise Pass:</b> Includes anything to do with the FREE
      <WikiLink page="Cruise Missions">Cruise Missions</WikiLink>.
    </p>
  </li>
  <li>
    <p>
      <b>Map Drop:</b> Reward upon completion of
      <WikiLink page="Category:Campaign">Campaign</WikiLink>
      (including Clearing Rewards),
      <WikiLink page="Combat#Hard Mode">Hard Mode</WikiLink>,
      <WikiLink page="Events">Limited Event</WikiLink>,
      <WikiLink page="War Archives">War Archive</WikiLink>
      Stages.
    </p>
  </li>
  <li>
    <p>
      <b>OPSI:</b> Reward from
      <WikiLink page="Operation Siren">Operation Siren</WikiLink>.
    </p>
  </li>
  <li>
    <p>
      <b>Shops: </b> Includes rewards (NO GEM SPENDING) from
      <WikiLink page="Shops">Munitions Shops</WikiLink>,
      <WikiLink page="Akashi's Shop">Akashi's Shops</WikiLink>, and
